{"tid":1143932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【何必做樓奴？】筍盤！ 意西西里島小鎮賤賣吉屋 每間$8.7港元但要負責翻新","createTime":"2019-05-07T23:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T09:57:47.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8908455fd170da31e6ceab12e50df5014c3ee243","tid":1143932,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T23:54:57.000Z","msg":"意大利西西里島南部市鎮穆索梅利（Mussomeli）政府眼見近年居民不斷搬走，導致鎮內現時有500間空置房屋，於是決定將空屋以超筍價1歐元（8.7港元）出售。<br />\n穆索梅利鎮政府現時率先在網上出售100間空置房屋，全部售1歐元（8.7港元），之後再售400間。但超筍價當然有附帶條件，就是買家必須在3年內自行翻新房屋，否則便會被沒收4697歐元（4萬港元）訂金。<br />\n翻新房屋估計每平方呎要花89歐元（775港元），另加管理費2348至3787歐元（2萬至3.2萬港元）。當地的建築師及工程師會能夠提供協助，但買家亦可選擇市外的其他專業人士幫忙。<br />\n雖然部份出售的房屋非常細小，但屋內都有多間睡房，而且可以飽覽村內美麗景色。穆索梅利位於巴勒莫東南兩小時車程，市內有拜占庭洞穴（Byzantine caves）、一座中世紀城堡及眾多古老教堂等景點。鎮內本來有1.1萬人口，但近年不少居民陸續搬走，導致500間房屋空置。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557214989_cf0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557214989_cf0c.jpg&h=0e742f86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557214989_c147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557214989_c147.jpg&h=d93c1e87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557214989_8387.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557214989_8387.jpg&h=606267ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557214991_ae7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557214991_ae7d.jpg&h=14877b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190507/59572820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F59572820&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8S7Tr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=cd6a19a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F59572820&h=6374ffcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190507/59572820</a>"},{"pid":"6410b7153213837a5b46fcc7e839000575e38e80","tid":1143932,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T23:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881e29b8f1467a4eaa927025aeed314c6149e206","tid":1143932,"uid":190928,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T23:58:14.000Z","msg":"西西里嘅賊仔惡到戰艦都偷得走，你自己諗吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf3d8730b79052b88b12a64ad671622edb52bc0","tid":1143932,"uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T00:17:18.000Z","msg":"住個度日日可以係屋頂跳黎跳去，好似水行俠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b5c3d01f210cbaca06d40e517e7a82e6517b25","tid":1143932,"uid":22553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T00:21:00.000Z","msg":"幾時發明到隨意門？香港返工，一開門就返咗外國屋企？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2c5e6692f57881782d8b6ac4df17474cfde720","tid":1143932,"uid":9230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T00:30:18.000Z","msg":"執襪帶累身家咪呢啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"